title: Bounding Leap
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A unit comprised entirely of models with this special rule Run and Charge an additional 3". In addition, a unit comprised entirely of models with this special rule treat units it charges as having Gone to Ground (if the targeted unit can Go to Ground).